title: Game Booster Portable 3.4.0
description:
Application: Game Booster
Category: Utilities
Description: Game Booster is a small program that you can use to optimize your PC for optimal performance (like if you want to play a game and its running slow, just 'switch to gaming mode' to get the most out of your computer). It works by temporarily stopping system processes and then, after you play that really good game, or run that really big program, you go 'back to normal mode'. Its really simple and yet so useful.
